<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
		<title>Désinscription newsletter</title>
	</head>
	<style>
		body {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			font-family: "Helvetica Neue", "Helvetica", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
			line-height: 1.6;
			color: #353535;
			background-color: rgba(53, 53, 53, 0.1);
		}
		.container {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			justify-content: center;
			align-items: center;
		}
		h1 {
			background-color: #353535;
			color: #fff;
			font-size: 2rem;
			margin-top: 0;
			padding: 1rem;
		}
		h1,
		h2 {
			text-align: center;
		}
		button {
			background-color: #353535;
			color: #fff;
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			padding: 1rem;
			border: none;
			border-radius: 5px;
			margin-top: 1rem;
		}
		section {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			width: 80%;
			margin-bottom: 5rem;
			margin-top: 5rem;
		}
	</style>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Bonjour
				{{newsLetter.email}}
				!</h1>
			<p>Voulez-vous confirmer la désinscription à la newsletter ?</p>
			<form method="post" action="{{ path('validate-unsubscribe', {'uuid': uuid}) }}">
				<input type="hidden" name="_token" value="{{ csrf_token('delete' ~ newsLetter.id) }}">
				<div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
					<button type="submit">
						Se Désinscrire
					</button>
				</div>
			</form>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
